# Removal of missing values at the beginning/end

Removal of missing values at the beginning/end

## Usage

``` r
clean_extremities(s)
```

## Arguments

- s:

  Original series

## Value

Cleaned series

## Examples

``` r
y <- window(ABS$X0.2.09.10.M, start = 1982, end = 2018, extend = TRUE)
y
```
